 Stark\">Benjen Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wun_Weg_Wun_Dar_Wun\" title=\"Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun\">Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_39&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-Sea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hardhome\" title=\"Hardhome\">Hardhome</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">Haunted forest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mole%27s_Town\" title=\"Mole&#39;s Town\">Mole's Town</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">Narrow sea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightfort\" title=\"Nightfort\">Nightfort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Tower\" title=\"Shadow Tower\">Shadow Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>